  "article_text": "Welcome to the Star Atlas weekly recap from the Intergalactic Herald. Below is what happened with Star Atlas this past week.\nWe are looking for guests to be on our podcast. The podcast is a discussion of the past week’s news about Star Atlas. If you are interested in being on the podcast, please contact us.\nWe are launching a Star Atlas merch store. Please check it out at Intergalactic Gear.\nWe are creating a “non-guild” guild. If you are interested in learning more, please go to Intergalactic Coalition.\nIf you would like to support our efforts, donations can be sent to intergalacticherald.sol\nMetaverse Nomads #153 – Star Atlas/Honeyland All 100 SFTs Created\nMetaverse Nomads posted a video of their weekly Star Atlas livestream.\nWEEKLY STAR ATLAS NEWSLETTER #136\nAephia published their weekly Star Atlas newsletter.\nStar Atlas: Recap 6-30-24\nBeyond the Horizon posted a video recapping the latest in Star Atlas.\nAtlas Brew #118\nStar Atlas TV posted a recording of the latest Atlas Brew.\nStar Atlas Townhall #43\nStar Atlas TV posted a recording of the Star Atlas Townhall.\nStar Atlas – A Universe Coming to Life (WORK IN PROGRESS)\nDominicVain posted a video of some work in progress for Star Atlas.\nStar Atlas Economic Report 2024 Q2\nStar Atlas published their quarterly economic report.\nTOWN HALL REPORT – JULY 3, 2024\nAephia published a report of the latest Star Atlas Townhall.\nThe Mega Star Atlas Town Hall Recap – July 3, 2024\nHologram News Network published a recap of the latest Star Atlas Townhall.\nStar Atlas: July 4th Town Hall Recap\nBeyond the Horizon posted a video about the latest Star Atlas Townhall.\nTown Hall #43 – Recap\nStar Atlas published a recap of their Townhall.\nSTAR ATLAS #241 BEST TOWN HALL – Initial Reactions!\nMetaVerse Explorer posted a video of his reaction to the Star Atlas Townhall.\nStar Atlas – Command Deck : SA Townhall Updates, today with Krigs (Hologram), MUD Empire..! !disco\nNebularTV posted the lasted 